x4freetext: Deuterons on deuterium for 11 MeV neutrons
Deuterons on tritium for 24 MeV neutrons
Beam pulse duration checked by scattering from gold
Incident neutron energy spread due to:
6.6-meter flight path used. Main detectors placed
inside water tank to insure radiation shielding. Front
of water tank shielded by iron and paraffin and used
a copper shadow bar. Computer code PKFIT used to
extract peak areas from time of flight.
Data were corrcted for dead time, source anisotropy,
neutron flux attenuation and multiple scattering.
